I'm sorry.

4
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,680
You know, there was a time

5
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,560
I think it was the past couple of years

6
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:05,000
when I suddenly felt that our lives

7
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,159
were pretty meaningless

8
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,000
Maybe suddenly you have everything.

9
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,960
You have money.

10
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,719
You have a house.

11
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,520
You have a car.

12
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,199
And the child is so adorable.

13
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,159
When everything goes smoothly all of a sudden,

14
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,560
