15
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:31,280
It even gets a bit boring.

16
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:37,560
But after what happened to you this time,

17
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,400
I just realized that

18
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,919
