22
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:08,639
Yes.

23
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:41,360
Mr. Liu, please come this way.

24
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,599
Open your mouth.

25
00:04:01,479 --> 00:04:03,560
Son, look how good your mom is to me.

26
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,759
You're so annoying. How do you know it's a son?

27
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:06,919
What if it's a girl?

28
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,759
I'm telling you, it's definitely a boy.

29
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:11,560
Let me ask you something.

30
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,599
The gas company called me.

31
00:04:14,639 --> 00:04:15,919
They said there's no money left in your account.

32
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,680
