33
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,319
I already paid the money.

34
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,240
Then where did your salary go?

35
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,399
I lent it to Liu Yang.

36
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,519
He said he needed the money urgently.

37
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,800
He'll pay me back after a while.

38
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,800
I need to take a work call.

39
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,759
Master.

40
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,279
Hello?

41
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:44,160
All the legal procedures for the An Pinghai case have been completed.

42
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:46,199
The death sentence will be carried out soon.

43
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,600
He requested to see you before the execution.

44
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:49,639
See me?

45
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,600
We'll talk about it later.

46
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,399
