Collective second-class merit.

61
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,800
All I got was a collective second-class merit.

62
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:07,480
You should know it was just a collective second-class award.

63
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:09,279
Would you still have risked your life to catch me?

64
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:12,079
Yes, definitely.

65
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:13,639
