77
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,680
Then let me say something.

78
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,000
Go ahead.

79
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:40,160
You're right.

80
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:42,279
I was scared.

81
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:45,199
And I should thank you.

82
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,279
The day after we caught you,

83
