86
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,279
A person only has one life.

87
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,000
Who isn't afraid of death?

88
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,399
I'm afraid too.

89
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,079
I was terrified at the time.

90
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,439
I was afraid my wife would lose her husband.

91
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,600
Afraid my child would lose their father.

92
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,839
Afraid my sister would lose her brother.

93
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,839
And afraid my father would lose his son.

94
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:22,600
But all of that was fear after the fact.

95
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,839
If I had to do it again,

96
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,040
I would still risk my life to catch you.

97
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,160
Are you out of your mind?

98
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,879
