408
00:21:49,319 --> 00:21:50,920
Don't worry, I'm even more concerned than you are.

409
00:21:51,319 --> 00:21:52,400
My sister is here with me.

410
00:21:52,839 --> 00:21:54,480
Alright, alright, I got it.

411
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,039
