427
00:22:41,119 --> 00:22:42,000
Forget it.

428
00:22:43,799 --> 00:22:46,119
Once someone gets involved with this stuff, it's all over.

429
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:51,480
The first time he came back from rehab,

430
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:54,920
