431
00:22:56,359 --> 00:22:57,640
And he really did change.

432
00:22:58,839 --> 00:23:01,039
No matter who invited him out, he wouldn't go.

433
00:23:01,599 --> 00:23:02,640
He came home on time.

434
00:23:04,319 --> 00:23:05,680
One day, it was his birthday.

435
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:09,240
A few friends called to celebrate.

436
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:11,039
I told him to go.

437
00:23:11,319 --> 00:23:12,319
Have some fun.

438
00:23:12,319 --> 00:23:13,480
Go out and get some fresh air.

439
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,680
It was just that one day.

440
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:20,200
That very night, I got a call from the police station.

441
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,400
The second time he came back,

442
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:28,480
I still had hope in my heart.

443
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:33,279
But I didn't expect it to happen even faster this time.

444
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:35,640
It wasn't even a week.

445
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:38,880
The third time he came back,

446
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:40,319
he was like a completely different person.

447
00:23:42,079 --> 00:23:44,680
He lost his temper every day and smashed things.

448
00:23:48,759 --> 00:23:51,319
I tied him to the bed.

449
00:23:54,039 --> 00:23:55,039
He kicked me.

450
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:56,279
And hit me.

451
00:23:59,119 --> 00:24:01,440
When I saw him like that, I thought,

